Package it.polimi.ingsw.model.powerup

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Newton
    this Class represents the Newton PowerUp can move one player in one direction for 1/2 moves
    PowerUp
    Abstract Class for PowerUps
    PowerUpDeck
    This class will be used to instantiate two decks of power ups one from which player draw cards and one that collect all discarded cards the deck will be swapped by the CurrentGame when one becomes empty
    TagbackGrenade
    This class represent the TagBackGrenade powerUp this card will give the target one mark, can be used only on a player that has just shot you
    TargetingScope
    This class represent the TargetingScope powerUp this card will add one damage to a target in a shoot action
    Teleporter
    This class represent the Teleporter PowerUp this card will teleport the player in any other cell of the map
